{"tid":1673471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遮打加泰集會真係失禮死人","createTime":"2019-10-24T16:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T16:20:41.000Z","uid":79304,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55874f04f322bda57cdef15f562f5dca3d216f16","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"人數少到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真我真係幾失望，成日對外宣傳話we connect we connect，但係呢幾日就吹曬風話<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港都未搞掂，點理人地呀？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">人地獨立喎，我地都唔係獨立唔好去</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">一陣比中共又有位入，過唔到人權法就唔好</span><br />\n我當講呢d野都係五毛洗板，算！<br />\n今晚見到既人數真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排CNN仲話我地既抗爭背後係一種高尚既情懆，一種更高既價值，但關於今次集會既討論就顯得好多人都只係顧自己。<br />\nConnect，自然有give and take，如果我地只係叫人關注我地，但就唔理其他國家既吶喊，舉曬籍口出黎叫自己唔好去，咁只係一路take，無give。<br />\n<br />\n難聽講句，果d「五毛」只係說話好聽d既中國蝗蟲，叫人幫我就得，幫人就唔得。<br />\n<br />\n加泰既情景與我地相近，要獲得國際支持，更加要顯出我地香港既核心價值係遠超想象。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n要緊記為自由抗爭的心<br />\n要自己去理解事情既背景<br />\n要用同理心去體諒別人<br />\n只要係受壓迫，被政權打壓，受不公義對待的，都係我地手足<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n時代革命，唔只係香港呢塊地方的革命，唔只係制度的革新，係思維，係每一個人都能獨立思考，同時又能互相成為共同體，然後一齊抗爭，爭取民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分地域，不分種族，不為計謀<br />\n連系著我們的只有公義和自由</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">We Connect</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下次唔好掛住聽風向啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己諗完自己行出黎啦手足"},{"pid":"d2acd973762329cd2f6bac4fa78aa3c8fc983f50","tid":1673471,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=20624dd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e9df0c4fdab585204be2da5806f33979693f2111","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2fe7599bdaeb83d86bf31312d266a380b5b6aaa9","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f45680917247419fc73e1b2469ce60be88efee5c","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cc0884e22732057e835764aca9d30bfad85e1f8d","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9cd8943bb9939da08656ec200cba61be96305fdd","tid":1673471,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"最後七日！！！！<br />\n香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃 Hong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a543a50f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding</a>"},{"pid":"f2c45b924411cdf0de2615bf6ca970e9b67832c3","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"下次手足要落多d力出黎集會啦，唔好怕中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271eb19542ba2c196c1beaefaf0b563afb74547e","tid":1673471,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"a82eea00d4d3ce34a750e9dd69f341020cd6ce7d","tid":1673471,"uid":79304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd8943bb9939da0865